extend layout


block main
  main#index
    h2= incorrectLoginMsg
    p The Dietary Food Journal web application provides you with three core functionalities.
    p First, you can add, update or remove food items from the food database. Second you can create a day by day journal documenting what you ate for breakfast, lunch, dinner, and snacks. Third you can review your journalto see what you ate.

block aside
  aside#index
    form(action='/login' method='POST')
      legend Login to Food Journal
      fieldset
        p
          label username
          input(type='username' name='username')
        p
          label password
          input(type='password' name='password')
        input(type='submit' value='login')
        
        p Don't have an account?
        a.small(href="/register") Register now